data.description: A rare move-in ready, two-story Dream Finder Homes gem in Harmony! This open floor plan provides a perfect backdrop to hosting, with the kitchen’s island opening to the dining area and great room. The kitchen is turn-key with a Whirlpool stainless steel appliance package, gas range and hood, quartz counters and walk-in pantry. Generously sized great room features a gas brick fireplace. The laundry room upstairs has tons of storage, washer and dryer are included.  Primary bedroom can fit a full King sized furniture set with room to spare and boasts a walk-in closet, with en-suite bathroom and linen closet. The amply sized second bedroom also has a walk-in closet. Fully fenced and landscaped backyard (6000 sq ft lot) has ample space for whatever suits your vision. Harmony’s impressive community includes a new community center, pool, fitness center, parks, trails, and dog park.  Between this beautiful home and the impeccable community, the possibilities are endless in making this place your own.
